comment: Burke (UTA) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Johnson's (MIA) driving layup.
Hayward (UTA) does not push off Winslow (MIA) as he creates space for the jump shot.
Dragic (MIA) does not push off Burks (UTA) on the perimeter.
Favors (UTA) commits a take foul on Whiteside (MIA).
Johnson (MIA) establishes legal guarding position. The contact made with Burks (UTA) is incidental and does not affect his drive to the basket.
Bosh (MIA) blocks the layup attempt by Burks (UTA) into the backboard.
Hood (UTA) commits a take foul on Dragic (MIA).
RATR shows that Favors (UTA) and Whiteside (MIA) briefly engage and then separate during rebounding.
L-Slash shows that Winslow (MIA) makes contact with Hayward's (UTA) wrist and the contact affects his jump shot.
Burks (UTA) commits a take foul on Dragic (MIA).
Deng (MIA) makes incidental contact with Hayward (UTA) and does not affect his ability to secure the loose ball.
Hayward (UTA) commits a take foul on Dragic (MIA).
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court of a successful 3 point field goal prior to the clock expiring was upheld.
